Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to 'Request Payment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time for cases involving 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Average resolution time for 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' in cases where it leads to 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and the next activity in the process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Total resolution time of cases with 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' leading to a re-submission ('Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE')
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time it takes from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to 'Payment Handled' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average waiting time to 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' from the start of the process
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' in cases successfully concluding with 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'
